Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西怪怪的  我不知为啥有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视中正在播放的  是跟我一点关系都没有的同县选手的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥我正支持着正处于落后的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又不知为啥觉得差不多春日要搞点事出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两点整全员在车站前集合  老老实实地过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连一句话都没说上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你说带东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套泳装  还有足够的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一定要骑自行车来  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我连一句话都没说上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像又知道春日打算要说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说  是感觉之前好像出现过完全相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的「既视感」么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就这样缴枪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虚！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿点干劲出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  全都到齐了  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这准备的架势来看也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天当然要有夏天的样子  要做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的时间可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在就要行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个只有一次的高一的暑假里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便我们是骑自行车去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也骑来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  自行车只有你和我的两辆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  阿虚  可不能输给古泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  立即出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你们两个赶紧停好车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说阿虚  接下来是要玩啊  你怎么就筋疲力尽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的错啊  谁的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这消毒液的气味  真给人一种实在的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  来游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛哦比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫同学  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺欢乐的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很欢乐的情景  还真让人感到和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得  凉宫同学也学会了有常识性的娱乐方法了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打个电话过来  单方面地说有事就挂的邀请方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不能说得上是常识性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那点事  要我说根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得那么开心的凉宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会做什么震动这个世界的事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为从初春开始就发生了太多事情 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得有点神经质了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又输了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希  我们再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  与其说是市民泳池  倒是个更适合平民泳池这名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么春日会选这样一个地方来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  与其说是市民泳池  倒是个更适合平民泳池这名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么春日会选这样一个地方来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  然后春日说了这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个就是我的团员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么他们都会听的  所以随便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩水中足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  这种事也常有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既视感什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余不多的暑假该如何度过的预定表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然发现  暑假只剩下两个星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后要赶快地去玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在不到两周内搞完这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠有什么想要做的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捞…金…鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  明天开始实行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近什么地方有盂兰盆会么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烟花汇演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了捞金鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是我给钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  其实也没有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近如何  精神好么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打搅你了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  为什么我会去和长门搭腔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  将我的懒觉夺走的又是春日的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是说找到盂兰盆会的会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  地点似乎是市民运动场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  今天你又是最后一个  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了  我们大伙一起去买浴衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日进了女装的大卖场之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自为朝比奈学姐和长门挑选了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后毫不客气地冲进了试衣间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我们等了大约一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人终于出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都非常合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦  是我给挑选的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱  太可爱了  真不愧是我挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐  转过来！转过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这么热闹真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂兰盆会啊  真亏得能聚集起这么多人…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  怎么又是这种感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有你想要玩的捞金鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捞个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去玩吧  来一决高下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个来  长门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  长门  你对那种东西有兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥有种受她照顾的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那种程度的我来买就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不需要那么多  就只要了一条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃一个的话没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那面具哪里弄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下来玩烟花吧  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是夏天  在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  虽然极力想要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有件事情却让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  明天是捉昆虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  虽说玩也没问题  你暑假作业做完了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么嘛  那种程度的作业有三天不就全部做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three days！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种麻烦事就得事先赶紧收拾掉再玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是正确的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种家伙脑子这么好  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天对于人的参数调整还真是随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  明天去捉昆虫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的虫子最多的那个人  怎么好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就把团长的权力让给他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣呢  只要是虫子的话什么都可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…只能抓蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这就是SOS团内部的捉蝉大战！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  是个让人有种「连这也是啊」的感觉的大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团内部的捉蝉大战就在这大晴天下进行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说大家都在努力奋斗  可应该说不出所料还是说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜者是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  还是要有放生的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它们一条生路  以后说不定会来报恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉来了到底能为我们做些啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回山里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点打开了盒子的潘多拉的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢…欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  我们在一无所知的情况下被套上了青蛙的罩衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始在超市的门口兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这待遇差算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长大叔也谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:12:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在实玖瑠的份上说送给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就为了这种东西累死累活地干活么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把这放在社团室做纪念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  你想什么时候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我许可的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  夺去了我的安眠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有非常不好的事情…这样下去我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:13:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会这个时候跟朝比奈学姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有点情况  你能现在就过来么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋  你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了  朝比奈学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了未来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  事情是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在永久地重复着同样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你满面春光地把那种非现实的话说出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  你知道自己在说什么吗  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  相当清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才和朝比奈学姐谈了下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是叫上我啊  然后你好回去了  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:15:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后意识到最近这里时间的流动出现了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该说是朝比奈学姐的功绩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托她的福我也确信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确信什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经重复体验同样的时间许多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刚才就听你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说应该是八月十七日到三十一日之间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正处于一个没有尽头的暑假的正当中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在确实是暑假…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对无法结束的Endless Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个世界里  九月一日之后的时间全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要谁相信那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望至少你能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被困在那个叫什么封锁空间里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一部分的时间被分割开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:16:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到八月三十一日二十四时整的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被重置  再回到十七日的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  全人类的记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也会重置  会重头再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是关于时间这个那个了的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…既然未来人也混进来了  那我觉得也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这件事和朝比奈学姐没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凉宫同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然本人没有这个自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心里什么地方总在想着暑假不要结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥啊  难道留着什么遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许她是想着暑假还有什么事情剩下没做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个\N会把一些莫名其妙的事情展开到大宇宙规模的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了这个的话  就能迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我就觉得  你好像乐在其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知你是不是也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近频繁发生的既视感之迷终于解开了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想来  那只能理解为是由于记忆重置而散落下来的残渣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道说全世界的人都感觉得到这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是这样  我和你算是特例了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那春日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙多少有一点意识到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说有了反而糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  别说是既视感了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该有一个人保存着所有轮回中的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊  那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说也该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带问下  这重复现在到底是第几次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是第15527次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  你在说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那话是认真的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多的次数  我们全都在重复同样的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非全部如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15527次中没有去盂兰盆会的模式  有第2391次和第11054次的这两次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  去了盂兰盆会而没有捞金鱼的模式有437次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工的有9052次  其内容有6个模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了发放气球  还有搬货物  做收银员  发送传单…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15527次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门她这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上两周的话就是…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是595年的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么长的时间仅她一个人能够好好地保留着记忆  无数次无数次地重复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  你到底到现在为止都是以什么样的心情度过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天是观测天体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是长门的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天体望远镜由古泉准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类第一次踏上火星的时候  一定会从暗处跑出来欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「欢迎来到火星」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找UFO吧  UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底想做啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道的话  也能顺利解决了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试下这样怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面突然抱住凉宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她耳边轻语「I love you」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这由谁来做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你没有适合的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I…I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不要  我要摆脱这种支配
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我来做怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的了  我做这角色还不够格  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只会让凉宫同学增加无谓的混乱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之后去了打击中心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  长门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在朝比奈学姐说出来之前就注意到了这轮回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的工作是观察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒涛般的暑假活动消化体制还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花大会  钓虾虎鱼大会  试胆  电影连看后是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在活动来活动去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我觉得春日应该不会这样就满足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此  也没有什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样终于来到了  八月三十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这样课题就如实地完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也就这样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  还有什么想做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暑假已经做了好多事了  已经很充实了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该还没有满足才对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天当预备日先空下来了  大家就这样休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天在社团教室再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  春…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天当预备日先空下来了  大家就这样休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还前所未有地强烈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能让春日回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重复了一万几千次的两星期又要陷入永远循环的窘境了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我该做什么呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春日的话里应该有提示的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  我想不起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业  还没动过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢  怎么都成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再重复的话  作业做了也没意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管明天来不来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  也只能交给那时的我来处理了吧


